Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  美國職大聯盟的總冠軍被稱作世界冠軍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談到日本棒球總決賽我就想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是美國國內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要自稱世界冠軍就先來把我們的球隊打倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是相當的臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「在說上一話的司嗎？話說她們怎麼經常說些很臭的東西啊」by 電車色狼]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鏡  美幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  此方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教教我這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊  你竟然來問有關學習的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面還有不少困難的題目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是街機問答遊戲的題目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長國文之類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也好好用心勉學一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是備考生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  哈  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這邊是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊我可是被稱作賢者的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就到那個甚麼ACADEMY上學去算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（QUIZ MAGIC ACADEMY：猜謎魔法學院系列遊戲，\N2003年由KONAMI發售，可以向全國聯網對戰。）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣所以有點睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩到幾點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美幸你一直都11點睡覺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}（多睡的孩子長得快）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  看到美幸我就這樣想了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小豐你也睡得不少  可就是不長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她就這麼說出來了  明明人家很在意的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}（當晚、9點）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思晚上打攪了  我是小早川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是岩崎同學家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  請叫一下小南…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 已經睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都這麼早睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぺったん　らんら　もじペったん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ふたりのもじぴったん：目前為「ことばのパズル もじぴったん」的系列曲。\N作詞：後藤裕之，作曲：神前曉，第10話中有捏到過。）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你唱得真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  對對  應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我就這麼告訴爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在奠基儀式之後  嗯  對對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  您又來…我還未成年呢  真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  沒有那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那麼再見  好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你手舞足蹈對方也看不到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習慣啦  習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來打電話的時候集中精神講話  玩遊戲的手就不得不停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過空閒的這只手異常的寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我懂我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  之前在打電話的時候就一直在用清潔滾子清理地板上的灰塵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軲轆軲轆滾個不停的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確能打發時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像無意義的塗鴉一樣的單純行動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一放下電話就沒精力再做那種事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像只有自己周圍的地板變得乾乾淨淨而有些悲哀似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你堅持把它掃完不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同對話  熱情也一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是扔下不管了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙相當的臭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾還覺得不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  ○cky  Poc○
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Pocky：吸管的樣子看起來很像餅乾棒）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我做過啊  上小學時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你是小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過  說到小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有粘上酸奶做成「麵包工廠」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵包工廠？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的「麵包工廠」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害羞  說出來聽聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一學期借你的那遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有別人想玩了  還我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  那個小不點？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說起來那傢伙也借了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該讓她還了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  柊你好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼…只是在這之前翻出好幾套不知道是問誰借的軟件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以覺得你還能記得真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有自己不記得借給誰了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想懶到甚麼程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  「債主忘卻法則」是絕對存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是宇宙公認心理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小柊  是我  美紗緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  真有你的  波將金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（戰艦波將金號：1825年蘇聯著名黑白無聲電影，15話中此方的夢話裡吐過一次）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  出甚麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  沒事沒事  稍微有點…抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  要事是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  甚麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然重要就別忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看了一下彩票抽獎的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都落空了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不太可能中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也寄出了不少明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都沒有中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄了這麼多還不中  總讓人懷疑是不是賣的人或者編輯在搞鬼啊甚麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此方  不可以這麼隨便懷疑別人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  今天就先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡之前先去一趟廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的話裡廢話很多  但這個沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日本搞笑藝人小島意雄的逗哏名句）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛明明那麼睏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可為甚麼說了笑話詞之後就變得這麼清醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}（翌日、深夜）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不能熬夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不想上廁所了  趁著瞌睡的時候早點睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才明明那麼睏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼只因為進被窩時的冰冷感覺就變得清醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}（又之後的一天、深夜）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚很暖和  能馬上入睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼只有腳暖烘烘的  睡不著啊  這是為甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到這種事情的  只有我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky★Star
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到了吃烤紅薯的好季節了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  小鏡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  我明白的  求你不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  不過會長胖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個叔叔的目光對上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不買的話不是有點說不過去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  那個「你要買不買啊」「不買真是讓人傷心啊」的視線…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Comiket上目光對上後很不好把書再放回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算比喻的牛頭不對馬嘴也照說不誤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  這是在展位前看書的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在售貨員面前拿起書  不買的話再擺回去的感覺很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過結果還是放回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近動畫化的輕小說增加了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前借你的小說  被做了3季的動畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:10.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這裡很可能說的是《全金》系列）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且新刊也快出了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動畫我雖然有看過  但是小說卻還沒讀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿頁的字看著就累
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來嗎你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經常玩的遊戲的字才多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確應該是這樣  真是不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆直接出Gal遊戲才能讓我得救了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  4季的動畫要甚麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼  這也是甚麼捏它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小豐  你一直都在做甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不管怎麼蓋都是斜著的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  的確有這種人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是有些笨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常這樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這種可愛的缺點和美幸真像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  姐姐果然好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次打不開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一樣擰緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開袋子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不從鋸齒處撕開好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會打開的  稍微等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire！…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算啦  我看還是從鋸齒處撕或者用剪刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那樣的話就感覺自尊心甚麼的輸掉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  蚊子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是感覺有甚麼在周圍撲騰就夠讓人心煩的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在被叮之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道了它的存在  就不得不出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是捕蚊人的本能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然在想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我或小豐被同學年的人告白的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就算是蘿莉控了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是同學年  說不是也算不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺在這種場合下重點是在外觀上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  難道說外表像小學生  實際上30歲的那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反  也可能喜歡大齡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有夠深奧的題目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要下定義很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是我家老爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鏡的話一定會說「反正都無所謂啦」就給打發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那爸爸你是怎麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷上那樣的媽媽  喜歡這樣的女兒  就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你是蘿莉控嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是小小的孩子  我也喜歡普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能說「也算蘿莉控」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之就是說要看角色而定的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣都是廢柴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爸爸你總是和我黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我是男生的話你還會像現在這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  我已經很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女孩子真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…洗澡水差不多燒開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小豐你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風頭不對就趕人走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個子小小的  又和你是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像Gal遊戲的角色一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？ 彼方從小就很可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我能理解爸爸迷戀上媽媽的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但媽媽為甚麼會和你結婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「全怪你不理我  我才會變成這樣喜歡Gal遊戲的！」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼說了以後出乎意料順利的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是威脅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  當然不光是這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此方你出生的時候我們可高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個痣  和宗君很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  眼睛和彼方你一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼看都是我們兩個人的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過希望這孩子長大後能普通些  而不要太像我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少身材別像我  性格別學宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嚴格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為甚麼突然問彼方的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我不太清楚媽媽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此方  媽媽不在了…寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有  爸爸一個人就抵兩個人的熱鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還有小豐在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方  此方已經長成一個好孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和你所期望的普通稍微有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:01.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小不點宅女）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  此方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  此方你可千萬別死在我前頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我是絲毫沒有這樣的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然彼方很年輕的時候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最後還是很幸福的笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然活著的一方很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我臨終的時候也想這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑著去…要甚麼樣的死法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌死之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你絕對會不得好死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  今天為了工作的資料收集買了臺數位相機…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好久沒有回到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在正在做甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好  來  笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  再來一張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了吧  話說爸爸你貼太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊  此方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得用新相機來拍紀念照嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用來收集資料的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說的那麼生硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:25.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  宗君真是一點沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來以前就不注意別人的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂  給我滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼  真過分啊  此方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  一點也沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說起來  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱起來的感覺越來越像彼方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要光明正大地講那些危險的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  我可以想像媽媽過去的辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  雖然你爸爸那個樣子  也不能學壞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  對了  此方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子那個遊戲通關了的話  也教教爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個難度意外的高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  父女一起玩遊戲  關係真的要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是不能入手我看中的角色的H Sence呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃哇…你讓女兒做甚麼啊  老公！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧  沒有進行錯誤的情操教育吧  宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  媽媽為甚麼選擇了爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  像這種宅男蘿莉控色迷迷的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般沒人會選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得這麼過分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真夠嚴苛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.73,0:17:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…也是啊  彼方她直感很敏銳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直忘記掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為甚麼會和這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣的廢柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我唯一的  絕對有自信的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對有自信的地方？ 那是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔？嗯呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是——「我是這個世界上最愛彼方的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這點…果然…受不了他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認同我的一切長處和缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將自己的一切長處和缺點都展示給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最能安心的地方——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最能使我安心的地方——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  多令人懷念呀  再拍一張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會和小豐一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對現在自己不能在那個地方多少有些遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦  一張已經足夠了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:26.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你果然還是因為嗜好才買的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說甚麼啊  爸爸我只是取材之前把它用熟練了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  就如同我心中有宗君你們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然活在宗君你們的心中的話
